    (function () {
      var el = document.getElementById("srf-browser-unhappy");
      var closeBtn = document.getElementById("srf-browser-unhappy-btn-close");

      function handler() {
        var d = new Date();
        // we don't use max-age here because it's not supported by IE < 9
        d.setTime(d.getTime() + 2592000000); // 30 days
        document.cookie =
          "browser-unhappy-closed=true; expires=" +
          d.toGMTString() +
          "; path=/; domain=.semrush.com;";
        el.setAttribute("class", "srf-browser-unhappy--hide");
      }

      if (closeBtn.attachEvent) {
        closeBtn.attachEvent("onclick", handler);
      } else {
        closeBtn.addEventListener("click", handler);
      }
    })();
